      "abstract": "Requires the Department of Land and Natural Resources to acquire by eminent domain the fee simple interest in the Pali Lanes property.  Appropriates funds for the just compensation of the acquisition of the fee simple interest in the Pali Lanes property by the Department of Land and Natural Resources."
